多次就冇人知了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2122782/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2122782/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"18c20a32392b14dd8a41db264b9d0bef9c488b0a","tid":2128750,"uid":177578,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f1c030cc9f1ab3e547dcd5137e4f11640d18745f","tid":2128750,"uid":158735,"like":143,"dislike":1,"score":142,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"咪唔好承認囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"承認中國學歷及資格<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bd3b51d2b759ca30dd18c36ed17e419287f433","tid":2128750,"uid":256019,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"人地全世界大部份都承認英聯邦專業資格，甚至以佢為標淮，你反而唔承認，咪愈黎愈變第三世界地區！不過講過就做，千祁唔好縮呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf5c06d4de0750158852c276a8686d617823979","tid":2128750,"uid":177217,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"假新聞嚟"},{"pid":"03b555e832c97e89e57fcdd4106237ac361c2176","tid":2128750,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:10:35.000Z","msg":"唔認晒五眼丫笨，跟住所有五眼畢業果啲政府職員全部炒晒去"},{"pid":"293a78843393bbad66780d29e683dbc6df9321c5","tid":2128750,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:10:40.000Z","msg":"認真，一定唔會。<br />\n<br />\n成班黑警狗官土共，個個送仔女去英國讀書。玩英國？唔通真係覺得石頭多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec39568cbbdf5b0def6b94b96362ec3ed23b3e2","tid":2128750,"uid":160147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"消息人仕透露？？？？？"},{"pid":"13d4228011bbbdaa3f967135eccdc8dc6ceab875","tid":2128750,"uid":8257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"74cf6969054744032d01b1e